    "innerHtml": "Who hath desired the Sea—the immense and contemptuous surges?<br>The shudder, the stumble, the swerve ere the star-stabbing bowsprit merges—<br>The orderly clouds of the Trades and the ridged roaring sapphire thereunder—<br>Unheralded cliff-lurking flaws and the head-sails' low-volleying thunder?<br>His Sea in no wonder the same—his Sea and the same in each wonder—<br>His Sea that his being fulfils?<br>So and no otherwise—so and no otherwise hill-men desire their hills!"
