    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'Air and water are good, and the people are devout enough, but the food is very bad,' Kim growled; 'and we walk as though we were mad—or English. It freezes at night, too.'"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'A little, maybe; but only enough to make old bones rejoice in the sun. We must not always delight in soft beds and rich food.'"
