  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'But he is my disciple. What else?'"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'He has told me.' Mahbub choked down his touch of spleen and rose laughing. 'I am not altogether of thy faith, Red Hat—if so small a matter concern thee.'"
  },
  {
